data.description:
Welcome Home to this unique log home! This home features vaulted ceilings, an open concept living room, dining room, kitchen, and family room areas. The original log home was a 3 bedroom 2 bathroom ranch and an addition was added off the dining room in the back which added a family room, a larger primary bedroom, a basement with an additoinal bedroom, 3/4 bath and a rec room. 
This home is located on a large lot (over 1/4 acre!) and is on a quiet street that ends in a cul de sac. The neighborhood is located in an unincorporated area encompassed by Westminster (mailing address is Broomfield) just North of 92nd Ave and Wadsworth Blvd (NOT Wadsworth Pkwy).
UNINCOPORATED JEFFERESON COUNTY! NO City Taxes!! Close to schools, shopping, restaurants, reecreation and amenities. Near Highway 36 for direct access to Boulder and Denver.
